data.title: Jaya Bachchan objects to Vice President Jagdeep Dhankar's tone during Rajya Sabha session; he hits back saying, ‘I don’t want schooling’
data.meta_description: In a recent heated exchange during the ongoing Budget Session of Parliament, actor-politician and Samajwadi Party (SP) MP Jaya Bachchan had a tense interaction with Rajya Sabha Chair Jagdeep Dhankhar. This incident marked the second time during this session that their interactions have captured attention.
data.text:
In a recent heated exchange during the ongoing Budget Session of Parliament, actor-politician and Samajwadi Party (SP) MP Jaya Bachchan had a tense interaction with Rajya Sabha Chair Jagdeep Dhankhar. This incident marked the second time during this session that their interactions have captured attention.

August 09, 2024 / 15:26 IST
